Revision history for perl distribution Test-Mojo-Role-Selenium

0.16 2019-01-10T12:26:41+0900
 - Stop using delay() inside wait_until()
 - Fix default element description when passing in a hash
 - Improved wait_for() in the case where the element is not present on the page at all
 - Add support for passing in interval and timeout to wait_for()

0.15 2018-12-12T12:07:16+0900
 - Changed default driver from Selenium::PhantomJS to Selenium::Chrome
 - No longer EXPERIMENTAL

0.14 2018-03-08T21:04:31+0100
 - Forgot to remove Carp::Always #4

0.13 2018-03-08T20:49:34+0100
 - Test::Mojo::WithRoles is no longer required
 - new() can take config overrides #1 #3
   Contributor: tomk3002

0.12 2017-11-22T11:59:47+0100
 - Add ENV variable to override Test::Mojo host

0.11 2017-11-22T11:07:06+0100
 - Fix documentation order issue
 - Add support for finding elements by id, css, xpath, ...
 - send_keys_ok() add the keys sent to default description

0.10 2017-08-10T13:17:23+0200
 - Add screenshots() attribute

0.09 2017-04-26T16:10:23+0200
 - Add wait_for()

0.08 2017-03-28T11:31:21+0200
 - Add support for arguments in MOJO_SELENIUM_DRIVER

0.07 2017-02-13T18:31:29+0100
 - Add toggle_checked_ok()
 - Change click_ok() to move mouse to the element first
 - Change wait_until() to a test method

0.06 2017-01-05T14:58:18+0100
 - Add wait_until()
 - Add support for send_keys_ok(undef, ...)
 - Remove wait_for_url()
 - Do not build app if MOJO_SELENIUM_BASE_URL is set

0.05 2017-01-04T17:25:03+0100
 - Renamed skip_all_or_setup() to setup_or_skip_all()

0.04 2017-01-04T16:50:06+0100
 - Fix $t->app()
 - Add if_tx()
 - Add skip_all_or_setup()

0.03 2017-01-04T11:19:34+0100
 - Fix send_keys_ok() with special keys
 - Add live_value_is() and live_value_like()
 - Add wait_for_url()
 - Add missing method go_back(), go_forward() and refresh()
 - More robust send_keys_ok() for invisible elements

0.02 2017-01-04T09:26:41+0100
 - Add support for MOJO_SELENIUM_BASE_URL

0.01 2017-01-04T00:18:18+0100
